cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.IR, cs.LG 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques to detect personal health mentions in social media. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves data mining and information retrieval techniques, which are covered by cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also deals with population health analysis, which falls under cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). Finally, the paper involves machine learning techniques, which are covered by cs.LG (Machine Learning).
